data.description: Welcome to this two story corner lot home. Located in a Cul-de-sac! As you enter the home you will see the formal living room equipped with carpet and wood floors. continuing to the kitchen, you will find white countertops, tile flooring, and a lovely shade of blue cabinetry. Next you can appreciate the fireplace in the dining area with access to the bonus room, as well, as to the guest bathroom and laundry room, neutral paint through out. Upstairs, you have the master bedroom along with the master bathroom equipped with double sinks, and double closets. Down the hall, you will find the other two rooms with their shared bathroom. The backyard is upgraded with concrete through out and a shed for extra storage! Located near Mary Henley Park, no HOA, Solar home $127 a month (PPA). Sold as is, seller will not make any repairs. Close to grocery stores, Hemet Valley Mall, West Valley High School and much more. Don't miss out! book an appointment now.
